28:31.084 --> 28:32.503
<i>Phenomenal.</i>

28:32.586 --> 28:33.629
Bees?

28:33.712 --> 28:37.132
<i>- Oh. Oh, my mistake.</i>

28:37.215 --> 28:40.010
