30:15.689 --> 30:17.566
- so she couldn't be traced.
- Mmm.

30:17.649 --> 30:19.568
Uh, I'll look up "Azarov mine."

30:19.651 --> 30:21.945
I mean, she said her father
had a mine, right?

30:22.029 --> 30:24.197
- Yeah. Yeah, good idea.
- Mmm-hmm.

30:28.118 --> 30:29.745
She trying to get you out of Asheville?

30:29.828 --> 30:31.121
Fat chance.

30:31.204 --> 30:33.707
But just 'cause they haven't come yet,
doesn't mean they won't.

30:33.790 --> 30:35.417
Plan on talking to your parents?

30:35.501 --> 30:36.543
What's Asheville?

30:37.503 --> 30:40.714
Uh, it's like boot camp,
or military school.

30:40.797 --> 30:43.800
-You know, for bad kids.
-Are you even trying to find anything?

30:43.884 --> 30:45.469
Try some Russian shit.

30:50.432 --> 30:53.101
Hey, you sent me that Snapchat?

30:53.184 --> 30:55.812
-Oh, yeah.
-No, I don't want to look at that.

30:56.396 --> 30:58.065
I know. We're tracing her story.

30:58.148 --> 31:00.192
Like, nothing so far,
uh, except for the bus.

31:00.275 --> 31:02.068
- Which is huge.
- Yeah.

31:08.534 --> 31:10.326
You'll be there tonight, right?

31:13.497 --> 31:15.791
That guy thinks he's the shit, doesn't he?

31:16.541 --> 31:18.585
He's a fucking dick
if he doesn't come back.

31:26.051 --> 31:27.928
Come sit, baby.

